parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Front Seat Back Pivot Pin or Bolt Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front seat back pivot pin or bolt can cause the seat back to collapse or fall backwards, potentially leading to loss of vehicle control, accidents, or injuries.
symptoms: The seat back collapses or falls backwards
the seat back pivot pin or bolt breaks
the seat back does not lock in position
the seat back moves forward while braking
the seat back makes noise or cracks.
